<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idf6f1b340-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5" identifier="/us/usc/t46/s57504"><num value="57504">§ 57504.</num><heading> Charter or sale of vessels acquired by Department of Transportation</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Vessels transferred to or otherwise acquired by the Department of Transportation in any manner may be chartered or sold by the Secretary of Transportation as provided in this chapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idf6f1b341-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5">(<ref href="/us/pl/109/304/s8/c">Pub. L. 109–304, § 8(c)</ref>, <date date="2006-10-06">Oct. 6, 2006</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/120/1665">120 Stat. 1665</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
